---
// src/pages/terms.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Terms of Use - MoneyInFuture"
  description="Terms of use for MoneyInFuture financial calculators. Free to use, for educational purposes only."
>
  <div class="calculator-header">
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="calculator-description">Last updated: June 2026</p>
  </div>

  <section class="seo-content" style="max-width: 760px;">
    <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>By using MoneyInFuture, you agree to these terms of use. If you do not agree, please do not use this
      website.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Use of the Service</h2>
    <p>MoneyInFuture provides free financial calculators for personal, educational use. You may:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; line-height: 2;">
      <li>Use the calculators for personal financial planning and education</li>
      <li>Share links to calculator pages</li>
      <li>Export and download results for personal use</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">You may not:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; line-height: 2;">
      <li>Reproduce or republish the calculators or source code for commercial purposes without permission</li>
      <li>Use automated means to scrape or overload the website</li>
      <li>Represent MoneyInFuture's calculations as professional financial advice to clients</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Educational Purpose Only</h2>
    <p>These calculators are provided for educational and illustrative purposes only. They do not constitute
      financial, investment, or tax advice. See our full <a href="/disclaimer.html">Disclaimer</a>.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">No Warranties</h2>
    <p>MoneyInFuture is provided "as is" without any warranty, express or implied. We do not guarantee the
      accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of calculations. Use at your own risk.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>The design, code, and content of MoneyInFuture are the property of MoneyInFuture. Calculator formulas
      themselves are mathematical expressions in the public domain.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes
      acceptance of the revised terms.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These terms are governed by the laws of India.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions about these terms, <a href="/contact.html">contact us here</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
